# Template file for 'ggoled'
pkgname=ggoled
version=0.0.0~git20260218
_gitrev=086a0b0f20b4d7f963442599d9ce8db40cad3a77
revision=1
build_style=cargo
make_build_args="--package ggoled --package ggoled_app"
hostmakedepends="pkg-config"
makedepends="eudev-libudev-devel SDL3-devel"
short_desc="Put graphics on SteelSeries Arctis Nova Pro OLED screen"
maintainer="xinoip <xinoip@proton.me>"
license="GPL-3.0-or-later"
homepage="https://github.com/JerwuQu/ggoled"
distfiles="https://github.com/JerwuQu/ggoled/archive/${_gitrev}.tar.gz>${pkgname}-${version}.tar.gz"
checksum=9572906ee8810839110fe1538750de0f6c9fd3be5d8ddccdb51408ce4631b603

post_install() {
	vinstall "${wrksrc}"/11-steelseries-arctis-nova.rules 0644 /usr/lib/udev/rules.d
}

do_install() {
	cargo install ${XBPS_VERBOSE+${make_verbose}} --target ${RUST_TARGET} --root="${DESTDIR}/usr" \
		--offline --locked --path ggoled_cli
	cargo install ${XBPS_VERBOSE+${make_verbose}} --target ${RUST_TARGET} --root="${DESTDIR}/usr" \
		--offline --locked --path ggoled_app

	rm -f "${DESTDIR}"/usr/.crates.toml
	rm -f "${DESTDIR}"/usr/.crates2.json
}

